1
00:00:08,420 --> 00:00:10,820
♪Let me write the legend♪

2
00:00:10,820 --> 00:00:13,580
=Young Swordsman=

3
00:00:13,580 --> 00:00:16,580
=Episode 2=

4
00:00:25,160 --> 00:00:25,960
There's demonic energy nearby.

5
00:00:37,159 --> 00:00:38,159
Fly over the city.

6
00:00:42,260 --> 00:00:44,940
(Sang Yan, Sang Yu, Northern Evil Duo,
Demon Sect's Death Envoys)

7
00:00:53,439 --> 00:00:55,799
I thought you were someone impressive.

8
00:00:55,799 --> 00:00:59,240
Turns out you're just a rookie saberman.

9
00:01:03,000 --> 00:01:05,719
Sang Yu, let's get one thing straight.

10
00:01:05,760 --> 00:01:08,040
Save this guy's heart, liver,
lungs, and kidneys

11
00:01:08,079 --> 00:01:11,799
for me to enjoy with my wine.

12
00:01:11,799 --> 00:01:12,920
Don't worry, Sang Yan.

13
00:01:12,959 --> 00:01:15,000
I only want his brain.

14
00:01:15,000 --> 00:01:16,959
You can have the rest.

15
00:01:16,959 --> 00:01:18,319
Deal.

16
00:01:21,280 --> 00:01:22,719
This is all because of me.

17
00:01:22,799 --> 00:01:24,200
He has nothing to do with this.

18
00:01:24,359 --> 00:01:25,519
If you want to kill someone,

19
00:01:25,519 --> 00:01:26,799
come for me.

20
00:01:28,599 --> 00:01:29,400
Miss...

21
00:01:29,400 --> 00:01:30,680
I'll hold them off.

22
00:01:30,840 --> 00:01:32,359
Run as far as you can.

23
00:01:37,000 --> 00:01:38,439
Who would've thought this young couple

24
00:01:38,439 --> 00:01:40,120
would become a pair of doomed lovers?

25
00:01:40,120 --> 00:01:41,680
That's hilarious.

26
00:01:48,959 --> 00:01:50,280
The Northern Evil Duo
from the Demon Sect.

27
00:01:50,359 --> 00:01:51,719
They actually came to Gusu.

28
00:01:52,959 --> 00:01:55,000
Isn't that Peng Dasheng from earlier?

29
00:01:55,400 --> 00:01:56,840
He really won't give up.

30
00:01:57,200 --> 00:01:59,439
Xiao, you fought him earlier.

31
00:01:59,599 --> 00:02:00,799
What's his cultivation base?

32
00:02:01,439 --> 00:02:03,000
His qi sea is empty.

33
00:02:03,040 --> 00:02:04,560
He doesn't have a trace of inner force.

34
00:02:04,959 --> 00:02:07,400
At best, he's just a low-level saberman.

35
00:02:07,959 --> 00:02:09,240
The Northern Evil Duo, however,

36
00:02:09,840 --> 00:02:11,520
are far above the sixth rank
in cultivation.

37
00:02:11,960 --> 00:02:13,280
If they really fight,

38
00:02:13,439 --> 00:02:16,280
killing him
would be easier than crushing an ant.

39
00:02:16,639 --> 00:02:17,879
I think otherwise.

40
00:02:17,879 --> 00:02:20,240
He saw through
my snake gu technique so easily.

41
00:02:20,520 --> 00:02:22,199
He's no ordinary person.

42
00:02:28,039 --> 00:02:29,520
Why are you still here?

43
00:02:29,639 --> 00:02:31,039
You're not leaving either, aren't you?

44
00:02:33,599 --> 00:02:35,639
They killed my parents.

45
00:02:36,080 --> 00:02:39,159
They'll never stop coming after me
for this blood feud.

46
00:02:40,319 --> 00:02:41,680
But you're different.

47
00:02:42,000 --> 00:02:44,039
You don't have to die here with me.

48
00:02:44,400 --> 00:02:45,439
I can handle...

49
00:02:49,520 --> 00:02:50,639
He really ran?

50
00:02:51,520 --> 00:02:53,319
I thought he was going to play the hero.

51
00:02:53,520 --> 00:02:54,919
Turns out he's just

52
00:02:54,919 --> 00:02:56,520
a useless pretty boy.

53
00:02:57,639 --> 00:02:59,639
(Could I have overestimated him?)

54
00:03:00,199 --> 00:03:03,159
I really thought that guy was fearless.

55
00:03:03,159 --> 00:03:04,159
Turns out he's nothing but

56
00:03:04,159 --> 00:03:06,360
a heartless hypocrite.

57
00:03:07,120 --> 00:03:07,960
Beauty,

58
00:03:08,319 --> 00:03:10,639
if you agree to have some fun with me,

59
00:03:10,639 --> 00:03:15,080
I'll make sure you get a painless death.

60
00:03:15,840 --> 00:03:17,599
I would

61
00:03:17,800 --> 00:03:19,560
rather die
than bring shame to my family.

62
00:03:36,199 --> 00:03:37,000
Are you okay?

63
00:03:39,319 --> 00:03:40,680
A roasted sweet potato?

64
00:03:43,360 --> 00:03:45,879
Do you like it? It's for you.

65
00:03:46,120 --> 00:03:47,360
So, you didn't leave?

66
00:03:48,120 --> 00:03:49,199
Who said I left?

67
00:03:49,199 --> 00:03:50,319
You were just...

68
00:03:51,599 --> 00:03:52,159
Look,

69
00:03:52,479 --> 00:03:54,080
I found this sweet potato in the temple.

70
00:03:54,080 --> 00:03:55,159
It's roasted so well
that it's dripping with flavor.

71
00:03:55,159 --> 00:03:56,360
Throwing it away would be a waste.

72
00:03:57,159 --> 00:03:58,719
Want a bite?

73
00:03:58,960 --> 00:04:00,560
I think it tastes better
than my Master's.

74
00:04:01,159 --> 00:04:02,479
He actually stayed?

75
00:04:02,719 --> 00:04:04,120
I knew I wasn't wrong about him.

76
00:04:04,960 --> 00:04:06,599
He knew it was a dead end,
yet he stayed.

77
00:04:06,800 --> 00:04:07,960
He doesn't know his own limits.

78
00:04:08,360 --> 00:04:10,080
Maybe he really has a chance to win.

79
00:04:10,240 --> 00:04:11,319
Impossible.

80
00:04:11,479 --> 00:04:12,520
Him?

81
00:04:12,800 --> 00:04:14,719
A mere saberman with no inner force?

82
00:04:15,319 --> 00:04:16,319
If he wins,

83
00:04:16,519 --> 00:04:18,519
I will eat my hat.

84
00:04:19,519 --> 00:04:20,319
Peng Xiao?

85
00:04:20,519 --> 00:04:21,920
Sounds pretty heroic.

86
00:04:22,279 --> 00:04:23,399
Miss.

87
00:04:23,639 --> 00:04:24,519
Fine, fine.

88
00:04:24,519 --> 00:04:25,839
You're right. He won't win.

89
00:04:27,120 --> 00:04:30,720
You brat,
looks like you're determined to die.

90
00:04:32,959 --> 00:04:34,079
I hate nothing

91
00:04:34,160 --> 00:04:36,959
more than those who bully the weak.

92
00:04:37,360 --> 00:04:38,839
Especially you two.

93
00:04:39,079 --> 00:04:42,120
Neither man nor woman,
neither human nor demon.

94
00:04:42,480 --> 00:04:43,920
You two are unpleasant to look at.

95
00:04:46,480 --> 00:04:47,680
No one has ever dared

96
00:04:47,680 --> 00:04:50,199
speak to us like that.

97
00:04:50,560 --> 00:04:51,360
Soon,

98
00:04:51,480 --> 00:04:54,120
I'll make you kneel
and beg me to kill you!

99
00:04:55,639 --> 00:04:57,920
Miss, hide behind me.

100
00:04:58,000 --> 00:04:59,319
Don't come out unless I call you.

101
00:04:59,480 --> 00:05:01,319
Are you sure you can handle them?

102
00:05:01,639 --> 00:05:02,920
If I can't win, I'll run.

103
00:05:07,120 --> 00:05:08,079
Ugly freaks.

104
00:05:09,040 --> 00:05:10,560
Since leaving the mountain,

105
00:05:10,639 --> 00:05:12,600
this is my first real fight.

106
00:05:13,120 --> 00:05:14,720
I'll use you two to test my blade.

107
00:05:14,759 --> 00:05:16,120
You dare use us to test your blade?

108
00:05:16,360 --> 00:05:18,399
You must be tired of living.

109
00:05:23,439 --> 00:05:23,879
Hey, wait.

110
00:05:29,639 --> 00:05:32,360
You're already on the verge of death,
yet you still came here to die.

111
00:05:32,360 --> 00:05:35,000
I admit you've got guts.

112
00:05:37,519 --> 00:05:38,639
Wait a little longer.

113
00:05:48,800 --> 00:05:49,759
Are you done yet?

114
00:05:50,040 --> 00:05:51,000
What's the hurry?

115
00:05:51,480 --> 00:05:54,399
I'll send you two
to the afterlife right now.

116
00:05:54,639 --> 00:05:56,079
You're asking for it!

117
00:05:58,279 --> 00:05:59,519
Grim Ghosts Seize Souls.

118
00:05:59,720 --> 00:06:01,079
Death Messengers Claim Souls.

119
00:06:01,079 --> 00:06:01,959
- Activate!
- Activate!

120
00:06:08,560 --> 00:06:09,480
Rumor has it
that the Northern Evil Duo's

121
00:06:10,000 --> 00:06:12,240
soul-summoning technique
is beyond anything ordinary.

122
00:06:12,399 --> 00:06:14,360
I never thought they could summon
a Soul Wraith to fight alongside them.

123
00:06:15,319 --> 00:06:16,360
What's a Soul Wraith?

124
00:06:16,680 --> 00:06:17,600
When a person dies, they become a ghost.

125
00:06:17,600 --> 00:06:18,519
When a ghost dies,
they become a Soul Wraith.

126
00:06:18,639 --> 00:06:20,000
Anyone killed by a Soul Wraith

127
00:06:20,079 --> 00:06:21,199
will have their soul
destroyed completely.

128
00:06:21,199 --> 00:06:22,199
Not even the gods can save them.

129
00:06:22,879 --> 00:06:24,959
A Soul Wraith is formed from
three souls and seven spirits.

130
00:06:25,199 --> 00:06:26,319
It has no shape and no substance.

131
00:06:26,639 --> 00:06:29,160
He is just wasting his time.

132
00:06:29,160 --> 00:06:30,519
Isn't there a way to counter it?

133
00:06:31,639 --> 00:06:33,279
The Soul Wraith's true form
has to be destroyed first.

134
00:06:33,480 --> 00:06:35,439
Then its clones
will disappear on their own.

135
00:06:57,600 --> 00:07:00,079
Miss, while the Northern Evil Duo
are distracted,

136
00:07:00,240 --> 00:07:02,279
this is the perfect chance to strike.

137
00:07:03,199 --> 00:07:04,000
No need to rush.

138
00:07:04,360 --> 00:07:07,279
Didn't you notice
he still hasn't drawn his blade?

139
00:07:07,480 --> 00:07:10,360
You mean
he's still hiding his true strength?

140
00:07:11,319 --> 00:07:15,120
I just think he's no ordinary person.

141
00:07:24,560 --> 00:07:26,240
Break!

142
00:07:41,759 --> 00:07:43,480
He actually destroyed
the Soul Wraith with one strike.

143
00:07:43,759 --> 00:07:46,839
Looks like we underestimated him.

144
00:07:46,839 --> 00:07:48,639
He just got lucky.

145
00:07:48,720 --> 00:07:50,480
I'd like to see how long he can survive.

146
00:07:57,639 --> 00:07:58,079
Xiao,

147
00:07:58,639 --> 00:08:00,360
can you see through his martial arts?

148
00:08:04,319 --> 00:08:06,160
His movements are light and graceful.

149
00:08:06,480 --> 00:08:08,319
Every step and turn is like
willow fluff dancing in the wind.

150
00:08:08,639 --> 00:08:11,040
His movements are a bit like
Wudang's Cloud Ladder Step.

151
00:08:11,560 --> 00:08:13,360
But his blade technique
is completely different.

152
00:08:13,680 --> 00:08:15,120
Sometimes fierce and powerful,

153
00:08:15,639 --> 00:08:17,160
with the force to split mountains
and shatter stones.

154
00:08:18,120 --> 00:08:20,959
Sometimes flowing like clouds and water,
ever-changing and elusive.

155
00:08:21,079 --> 00:08:22,720
So, I can't see through his style.

156
00:08:23,199 --> 00:08:24,120
The strangest thing is,

157
00:08:24,399 --> 00:08:26,120
he clearly has no inner force.

158
00:08:26,199 --> 00:08:28,279
Yet every swing of his blade
carries astonishing power.

159
00:08:28,879 --> 00:08:30,480
He's truly impossible to read.

160
00:08:32,720 --> 00:08:35,200
No wonder he broke
my snake gu technique so easily.

161
00:08:35,559 --> 00:08:36,960
Looks like
he really does have some ability.

162
00:08:37,759 --> 00:08:38,919
You're not thinking

163
00:08:39,279 --> 00:08:41,120
of taking him under your command,
are you?

164
00:08:42,320 --> 00:08:43,240
Why not?

165
00:08:44,559 --> 00:08:45,440
He's nothing but

166
00:08:45,440 --> 00:08:47,200
a smooth-talking country boy.

167
00:08:47,559 --> 00:08:49,519
Born with no status,
from a nameless sect.

168
00:08:49,679 --> 00:08:52,720
And he doesn't have even
a trace of inner force.

169
00:08:53,080 --> 00:08:54,840
You want him
to lead the disciples of the Wudu Sect?

170
00:08:54,919 --> 00:08:56,039
I won't accept that.

171
00:08:56,960 --> 00:08:58,399
The Demon Sect has wreaked havoc
across the martial world.

172
00:08:58,879 --> 00:09:00,600
Our Wudu Sect
has suffered greatly because of them.

173
00:09:01,840 --> 00:09:04,399
Master sent me to recruit young talents
to fight the Demon Sect.

174
00:09:05,080 --> 00:09:06,559
When choosing talent,
we shouldn't be limited by convention.

175
00:09:07,200 --> 00:09:08,639
As the sect's Holy Envoy,

176
00:09:08,799 --> 00:09:10,200
you should have a broader outlook.

177
00:09:13,399 --> 00:09:14,720
Okay. Then when do we make our move?

178
00:09:15,759 --> 00:09:16,600
No rush.

179
00:09:17,039 --> 00:09:20,200
His true strength
goes far beyond what we've seen.

180
00:09:32,799 --> 00:09:34,000
What kind of blade technique is that?

181
00:09:34,000 --> 00:09:35,519
Why is it so strange?

182
00:09:36,440 --> 00:09:39,200
My Master created this blade technique
while he was using the restroom.

183
00:09:39,200 --> 00:09:40,519
It doesn't have a name yet.

184
00:09:40,639 --> 00:09:41,799
But today, I think

185
00:09:41,840 --> 00:09:42,720
I'll name it

186
00:09:43,000 --> 00:09:44,600
Evil-Duo-Crushing Blade.

187
00:09:44,639 --> 00:09:46,519
- You...
- You've gone too far!

188
00:09:46,639 --> 00:09:47,360
I'll kill you!

189
00:09:47,519 --> 00:09:49,759
Sang Yu,
this man is stronger than expected.

190
00:09:49,919 --> 00:09:51,200
We should avoid fighting him for now.

191
00:09:51,360 --> 00:09:52,519
Leave if you want.

192
00:09:52,519 --> 00:09:53,360
His life

193
00:09:53,519 --> 00:09:54,679
is mine to take!

194
00:09:54,679 --> 00:09:55,519
Sang Yu!

195
00:10:01,980 --> 00:10:02,780
♪Come on♪

196
00:10:06,180 --> 00:10:07,460
♪This battle, I won't retreat♪

197
00:10:07,620 --> 00:10:10,700
♪Listen, this heartbeat echoes♪

198
00:10:10,980 --> 00:10:13,780
♪Fate is nothing but a net♪

199
00:10:14,020 --> 00:10:19,820
♪Either be trapped by it
or tear it apart♪

200
00:10:19,940 --> 00:10:21,420
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

201
00:10:22,500 --> 00:10:24,780
♪Even if the world's cold stares
stand in my way♪

202
00:10:26,399 --> 00:10:27,480
Sang Yu!

203
00:10:28,260 --> 00:10:31,940
♪I am my own king♪

204
00:10:31,960 --> 00:10:33,559
You scumbag!

205
00:10:34,320 --> 00:10:36,120
I'll kill you!

206
00:10:39,480 --> 00:10:41,360
Blood Burns the Heavens!

207
00:10:42,240 --> 00:10:43,919
Slay the Gods
and Annihilate the Heavenly Dao!

208
00:11:22,960 --> 00:11:24,320
Blood Sacrifice Heaven-Burning Art!

209
00:11:25,159 --> 00:11:26,799
This technique comes from
the Demon Sect's forbidden scripture.

210
00:11:26,879 --> 00:11:28,480
It uses the caster's flesh
and blood as the source,

211
00:11:28,720 --> 00:11:31,039
burning away a lifetime of cultivation
to gain the power to burn the heavens.

212
00:11:31,360 --> 00:11:32,840
Its power is enough
to shake heaven and earth.

213
00:11:33,120 --> 00:11:34,519
Once this technique is used,

214
00:11:34,840 --> 00:11:36,039
the caster's meridians will shatter,

215
00:11:36,039 --> 00:11:37,240
until their blood runs dry
and their soul is destroyed.

216
00:11:47,399 --> 00:11:48,759
What chance does Peng Dasheng have?

217
00:11:48,840 --> 00:11:49,799
None. Not even the slightest.

218
00:11:49,960 --> 00:11:51,480
Even putting aside
that his qi sea is empty

219
00:11:51,480 --> 00:11:52,720
and he has no foundation of inner force,

220
00:11:52,919 --> 00:11:54,320
even if he had inner force,

221
00:11:54,759 --> 00:11:56,600
he still likely couldn't withstand
this Heaven-Burning power.

222
00:11:57,080 --> 00:11:57,879
Unless...

223
00:11:58,559 --> 00:11:59,360
Unless what?

224
00:11:59,840 --> 00:12:01,679
Unless his cultivation
is above the fifth rank.

225
00:12:02,159 --> 00:12:03,519
Then he might still
have a chance to turn the tide.

226
00:12:03,879 --> 00:12:04,600
But he's nothing more than

227
00:12:04,600 --> 00:12:06,159
an obscure saberman.

228
00:12:06,639 --> 00:12:08,080
How could he possibly
have such cultivation?

229
00:12:08,799 --> 00:12:11,759
So you're saying
he has no chance of winning at all?

230
00:13:23,360 --> 00:13:29,559
Sun-Splitting Slash!

231
00:13:44,180 --> 00:13:45,020
♪Come on♪

232
00:13:46,820 --> 00:13:48,580
♪This battle, I won't retreat♪

233
00:13:54,940 --> 00:13:55,420
♪Come on♪

234
00:13:58,940 --> 00:14:00,620
♪This battle, I won't retreat♪

235
00:14:02,580 --> 00:14:05,540
♪In worn-out clothes,
my hem still carries frost and dust♪

236
00:14:05,820 --> 00:14:08,740
♪Among the crowd,
who is laughing at my absurdity?♪

237
00:14:08,980 --> 00:14:11,820
♪They say my birth
has already decided my path♪

238
00:14:12,220 --> 00:14:14,820
♪But I refuse
to believe my birth decides my worth♪

239
00:14:15,340 --> 00:14:18,300
♪With one blade in hand,
I've weathered countless storms♪

240
00:14:18,540 --> 00:14:21,540
♪Covered in scars,
only to be called young and reckless♪

241
00:14:21,700 --> 00:14:24,620
♪If this world only bows
to status and bloodlines♪

242
00:14:24,780 --> 00:14:27,540
♪Then I'll break every rule
with a single slash♪

243
00:14:28,100 --> 00:14:31,420
♪Listen, this heartbeat echoes♪

244
00:14:31,460 --> 00:14:34,460
♪Fate is nothing but a net♪

245
00:14:34,500 --> 00:14:40,140
♪Either be trapped by it
or tear it apart♪

246
00:14:40,540 --> 00:14:42,580
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

247
00:14:43,140 --> 00:14:45,660
♪I don't believe
anyone is born above another♪

248
00:14:46,380 --> 00:14:48,780
♪Even this mortal body
dares to fight back♪

249
00:14:48,900 --> 00:14:52,580
♪I'll step on fate and grow beyond it♪

250
00:14:53,180 --> 00:14:55,300
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

251
00:14:56,220 --> 00:14:58,340
♪Even if the world's cold stares
stand in my way♪

252
00:14:58,500 --> 00:15:01,780
♪This blade will cut through
all worldly judgment♪

253
00:15:01,820 --> 00:15:06,100
♪I am my own king♪

254
00:15:19,180 --> 00:15:20,740
♪I emerge into the world♪

255
00:15:20,740 --> 00:15:22,500
♪Unknown, yet I dare
to shake the martial world♪

256
00:15:22,500 --> 00:15:23,860
♪My pride is my trump card♪

257
00:15:23,860 --> 00:15:25,660
♪Even if fate treats me as worthless,
I refuse to yield♪

258
00:15:25,660 --> 00:15:27,060
♪Born with a gift, I won't give in♪

259
00:15:27,060 --> 00:15:28,820
♪Against heaven's will,
I'll bet on my rise♪

260
00:15:28,820 --> 00:15:30,340
♪A sword in hand,
fresh out of the mountain♪

261
00:15:30,340 --> 00:15:32,060
♪I dare to break every rule♪

262
00:15:32,060 --> 00:15:33,380
♪I see through
the masks of human hearts♪

263
00:15:33,380 --> 00:15:35,220
♪Famous clans are nothing
but a few layers of disguise♪

264
00:15:35,220 --> 00:15:36,460
♪They kneel and beg for fame♪

265
00:15:36,460 --> 00:15:38,700
♪I stand and fight for my dignity♪

266
00:15:38,700 --> 00:15:40,220
♪Facing powerful foes, I will not bow♪

267
00:15:40,220 --> 00:15:41,820
♪With my blade in hand,
I decide what is right♪

268
00:15:41,820 --> 00:15:43,420
♪Stand for justice and never step back♪

269
00:15:43,420 --> 00:15:45,140
♪Even if the whole world
stands against me♪

270
00:15:45,140 --> 00:15:46,860
♪Untamed,
frost has carved me to the bone♪

271
00:15:46,860 --> 00:15:48,220
♪Only then do I become more like myself♪

272
00:15:48,220 --> 00:15:49,860
♪Fight, this life of mine is unyielding♪

273
00:15:49,860 --> 00:15:51,340
♪No matter how dark the martial world,
I'll walk through it♪

274
00:15:51,340 --> 00:15:53,060
♪For love, I do not fight for the world♪

275
00:15:53,060 --> 00:15:54,660
♪I only want
to protect her for a lifetime♪

276
00:15:54,660 --> 00:15:56,220
♪Carefree,
this fleeting life is but a brief stay♪

277
00:15:56,220 --> 00:16:00,540
♪Now I know all things can be overcome♪

278
00:16:00,540 --> 00:16:02,700
♪I raise my blade and change my fate♪

279
00:16:02,700 --> 00:16:05,300
♪Let me write the legend♪

280
00:16:10,180 --> 00:16:12,740
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

281
00:16:12,740 --> 00:16:16,060
♪Win or lose, strong or weak,
none of it matters to me♪

282
00:16:16,060 --> 00:16:18,540
♪Even if I fall, I will still shine♪

283
00:16:18,540 --> 00:16:22,620
♪Let my name
be carved into the vast world♪

284
00:16:22,980 --> 00:16:25,580
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

285
00:16:25,700 --> 00:16:28,060
♪If this world refuses to forgive me♪

286
00:16:28,060 --> 00:16:31,100
♪Then I'll burn away
all my edge and brilliance♪

287
00:16:31,100 --> 00:16:36,140
♪And trade it for a new dawn♪
